oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Nashville Songwriters Association International's Legislative Show (August 3, 2006)
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Bluebird Café (Restaurant : Nashville, Tenn.); Fund raising; Lyricists;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color lobby card (purple and yellow on light yellow) announcing the Nashville Songwriters Association International's Legislative Show featuring hit songwriters Chely Wright, Gary Harrison, Anna Owens, and Peter Cooper at the Bluebird Cafe on August 3. Proceeds from the event go towards NSAI's Legislative efforts, which support the rights of songwriters everywhere.
